   ->  Custom Scan (ColumnarScan) on _timescaledb_internal._hyper_1_3_chunk
         Output: _hyper_1_3_chunk."time", _hyper_1_3_chunk.device_id, _hyper_1_3_chunk.val
         Reverse: true
         ->  Sort
               Output: _hyper_1_3_chunk_compressed._ts_meta_count, _hyper_1_3_chunk_compressed.device_id, _hyper_1_3_chunk_compressed._ts_meta_min_1, _hyper_1_3_chunk_compressed._ts_meta_max_1, _hyper_1_3_chunk_compressed._ts_meta_v2_first_time, _hyper_1_3_chunk_compressed._ts_meta_v2_last_time, _hyper_1_3_chunk_compressed."time", _hyper_1_3_chunk_compressed.val
